ter throughout the day. Sometimes thirst is mistaken for hunger.\r\n\r\n',0),(35,'2024-05-21 02:01:52',32,'High street gym is wonderful','Let&#x27;s go to high street gym!\r\nLet&#x27;s go to high street gym!\r\nLet&#x27;s go to high street gym!\r\nLet&#x27;s go to high street gym!\r\nLet&#x27;s go to high street gym!\r\nLet&#x27;s go to high street gym!\r\nLet&#x27;s go to high street gym!\r\n',1),(36,'2024-05-21 02:28:37',32,'Let&#x27;s go to high street gym!!!','Let&#x27;s go to high street gym!!!Let&#x27;s go to high street gym!!!Let&#x27;s go to high street gym!!!Let&#x27;s go to high street gym!!!Let&#x27;s go to high street gym!!!Let&#x27;s go to high street gym!!!',1),(38,'2024-08-20 00:00:00',32,'Hiring Announcement: Eric Dong Joins Our Team as a New Trainer!','We are thrilled to announce that Eric Dong has joined our team as a new trainer! With his extensive background in fitness and passion for helping individuals achieve their health goals, Eric is a fantastic addition to our community.\n\nAbout Eric Dong\n\nEric brings a wealth of experience to our team, having spent over a decade in the fitness industry. His journey began with a degree in Exercise Science and has since evolved into a distinguished career as a personal trainer and fitness coach. Eric’s approach to fitness is holistic, focusing not only on physical training but also on mental wellness and motivation.\n\nWhat Eric Brings to the Team\n\nExpertise in Diverse Training Methods: Eric is proficient in a wide range of training techniques, from strength training and cardiovascular workouts to functional training and yoga. His versatile skill set ensures that he can cater to various fitness levels and goals.\n\nPersonalized Training Programs: Eric believes in creating customized fitness plans that align with each individual&#x27;s unique needs and aspirations. Whether you’re looking to build muscle, lose weight, or improve overall wellness, Eric is here to guide you every step of the way.\n\nInspi